Classes
Class
Description
addItemGUI
The addItemGUI class provides a GUI to add items to the selected VendingMachine.

The addItemSpecialGUI class provides a GUI for adding special items to the FriedRiceVM vending machine.
AddMoneyGUI
The AddMoneyGUI class provides a graphical interface for replenishing money in the selected vending machine.
BuyItemGUI
BuyItemGUI is a user interface for purchasing items from a vending machine.
ChoosePhotoGUI
This class represents the GUI for choosing photos for vending machine slots.
CreateVendingMachineMenu
This class represents the menu for creating a vending machine.
FriedRiceVM
The VendingMachineFactory.FriedRiceVM class represents a special vending machine for selling fried rice.
FrmSlot
The VendingMachineFactory.FrmSlot class represents a slot in a vending machine's inventory system with additional features like slot type and separate selling flag.
Item
The VendingMachineFactory.Item class represents an item with a name, price, and calories.

MaintainVM_Regular class represents a panel for maintaining regular vending machines.

This class represents a graphical user interface (GUI) panel for maintaining a Special Vending Machine (FriedRiceVM).

The VendingMachineFactory.MoneyManager class is responsible for managing money denominations and quantities.

This class represents a graphical user interface (GUI) panel for maintaining a Special Vending Machine (FriedRiceVM).

The TestVM_Main class represents a GUI panel for choosing an option to test a vending machine.

The TestVM_Regular class represents a GUI panel for testing regular vending machines.

The TestVM_Special class represents a GUI panel for testing special vending machines.

The TransactionSummaryPanel class displays a summary of transactions for a selected vending machine.

The VendingMachine class represents a vending machine that contains slots to hold items, manages money, and facilitates buying and restocking operations.
VendingMachineFactory
The VendingMachineFactory class is responsible for creating and managing vending machines.
